Southmark Corp said it acquired BergVentures Inc, which manages 84 apartment complexes with over18,000 units and 12 shopping centers stretching from New Jerseyto Florida that are controlled or affiliated with Berg HarmonAssociates. Terms were not disclosed.    Southmark said the acquisition makes it the nation'slargest apartment management firm with over 100,000 units underits wing. Southmark also said it has become the managingpartner of Berg Harmon Associates. Over 3,000 Berg HarmonLimited partners have made capital investments of over 300 mlndlrs in the properties now managed by Southmark.     Reuter&#3;